    dc:creator "Bertani, Rogério" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "Taxonomic revision and cladistic analysis of Lasiodora C. L. Koch, 1850 (Araneae, Theraphosidae) with notes on related genera" ;
    bibo:endPage "116" ;
    bibo:issue "1" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2023-12-27" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "5390" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434522>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434524>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434638>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434640>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434642>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434644>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434646> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434522>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8–15. Stridulatory setae of prolateral coxa I, males. 8, L. parahybana, Brazil, state of Pernambuco, Cabo de Santo Agostinho. 9, L. sertaneja n. sp. (IBSP 4127B). 10, L. camurujipe n. sp. (MNRJ 7764). 11, L. franciscana n. sp. (IBSP 8050). 12, L. subcanens (IBSP 9546). 13, L. klugi (MNRJ 7742). 14, L. benedeni (IBSP 84328). 15, L. klugi, Brazil, state of Bahia, Ilhéus. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434522/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434524>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Strict consensus of three cladograms obtained with setk.run and concavity 7.8125. All characters non-additive. Fit = 7.38251, length = 161.30. Absolute/relative Bremer support are in each node. The names of the genera and species in the cladogram are in accordance with the results obtained in the cladistic analysis carried out here, and do not consider the new genera and transfers proposed by Galleti-Lima et al. 2023." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434524/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434638>
    dc:description "FIGURES 203─208. Lasiodora camurujipe n. sp. (203─207) male holotype (MZUSP 78870). (203─205) left palp bulb. 203, retrolateral. 204, prolateral. 205, dorsal. (206─207) left tibial apophysis. 206, ventral. 207, prolateral. 208, female paratype (MZUSP 78871), spermathecae, dorsal. Scale bar = 1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434638/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434640>
    dc:description "FIGURES 209─213. Lasiodora camurujipe n. sp., male holotype (MZUSP 78870), stridulatory apparatus. (209─210) left maxilla, retrolateral. 209, general view. 210, detail of spiniform setae on upper, middle and lower areas. (211─213) left coxa I, prolateral. 211, general view. 212, detail of stridulatory setae. 213, detail of area below suture. Scale bar = 1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434640/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434642>
    dc:description "FIGURES 214─218. Lasiodora camurujipe sp. nov., female paratype (MZUSP 78871), stridulatory apparatus. (214─215) left maxilla, retrolateral. 214, general view. 215, detail of spiniform setae on upper, middle and lower areas. (216─218) left coxa I, prolateral. 216, general view. 217, detail of stridulatory setae. 218, detail of area below suture. Scale bar = 1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434642/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434644>
    dc:description "FIGURES 219─222. Lasiodora camurujipe n. sp., live. 219, male. 220, female, 221─222, immatures. All from RPPN Camurujipe, Mata de São João, state of Bahia, Brazil. Photos: Rogério Bertani." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434644/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434646>
    dc:description "FIGURES 223─224. Maps showing records of Lasiodora camurujipe n. sp. in the state of Bahia, Brazil. 223, relief. 224, biomes. Forested areas (Brazilian Atlantic Forest) of Fig. 224 are in green shades, pinkish areas are of Caatinga." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434646/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

